This is Perl module WRMX::Test.

INSTALLATION

WRMX::Test installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % cpan WRMX::Test

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

WRMX::Test documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc WRMX::Test

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

